Host *
    ControlMaster auto
    ControlPath $XDG_CACHE_HOME/ssh/%C
    ControlPersist 6h

    GSSAPIAuthentication no
    PasswordAuthentication no

    NoHostAuthenticationForLocalhost yes

    VerifyHostKeyDNS ask
    VisualHostKey yes

Host *+*
    ProxyCommand ssh-jump %h %p %r

